<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5380965>
    dc:description "FIG. 11. Wings of assorted genera of Cretaceous Tabanomorpha. A. Palaepangonius glossa, new species, JZC Bu-248. B. Athericites kensmithi (ex: Mostovski et al., 2003). C. Sinocretomyia miniscule (ex: J.-F. Zhang, 2012). D. Galloatherix incompletus (ex: Nel et al., 2014). Not to the same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5380965/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5381031>
    dc:description "FIG. 43. Palaepangonius glossa, new species (stem-group Tabanomorpha), holotype JZC Bu-248. A. Habitus, right lateral. B. Head, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5381031/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

